---
import Container from '../components/Container.astro'
import EmailForm from '../components/EmailForm.vue';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title='Contact' active='contact'>
  <Container>
    <div class='mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12'>
      <div class='contact-intro mb-8 rounded-lg bg-white p-8 shadow-md'>
        <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-900'>I'd Love to Hear From You!</h2>
        <p class='mb-4'>
          Thank you for visiting my website dedicated to the rich and delicious world of traditional
          Polish cuisine. Whether you're a lifelong fan of pierogi, a newcomer curious about bigos,
          or someone with a family recipe to share, I want to connect with you!
        </p>
        <p class='mb-4'>
          Do you have questions about my recipes? Looking for cooking tips or recommendations on
          where to find authentic ingredients? Maybe you have your own Polish food stories and
          traditions that you'd like to share with me. Whatever it is, Iâ€™m excited to hear from you!
        </p>
        <p class='mb-4'>
          Please fill out the form below to get in touch. Your feedback, questions, and stories are
          invaluable to me, and I can't wait to respond.
        </p>
        <p class='font-semibold'>Smacznego!<br />Darek</p>
      </div>

      <EmailForm client:load />
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>